header(class="sticky top-0 z-20 border-b border-zinc-200 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950/95")
    div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 px-5 py-4 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between")
        div
            div(class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-hard-drive")
                span Storage
            h1(class="mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 스토리지
        div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
            span(class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-md border px-2.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(cluster().status)")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-circle text-[7px]")
                | {{clusterStatusLabel()}}
            span(class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-md border px-2.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(health().status)")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-heart-pulse text-[11px]")
                | {{healthLabel()}}
            button(type="button", (click)="load()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right")
                span 새로고침
            button(*ngIf="operationDetail()?.id", type="button", (click)="openOperationModal()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-rectangle-list")
                span 실행 결과

main(class="space-y-5 px-5 py-5")
    div(*ngIf="loading()", class="h-32 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-5 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400") 스토리지 상태를 불러오는 중입니다.
    div(*ngIf="error()", class="rounded-md border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-rose-700 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-rose-950/40 dark:text-rose-300") {{error()}}

    div(*ngIf="!loading() && !error()", class="space-y-5", data-testid="storage-overview")
        div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 border-b border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800")
            button(*ngFor="let tab of tabs", type="button", (click)="setActiveTab(tab)", [disabled]="!tab.enabled", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 border-b-2 px-3 text-sm font-semibold transition-colors disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-45", [ngClass]="!tab.enabled ? 'border-transparent text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-600' : (isActiveTab(tab.key) ? 'border-zinc-950 text-zinc-950 dark:border-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-50' : 'border-transparent text-zinc-500 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400 dark:hover:text-zinc-100')")
                i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="tab.icon")
                span {{tab.label}}

        div(*ngIf="actionError()", class="rounded-md border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-rose-700 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-rose-950/40 dark:text-rose-300") {{actionError()}}

        section(*ngIf="isActiveTab('overview') && showMasterBootstrap()", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900", data-testid="storage-ceph-master-bootstrap")
            div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 px-4 py-3 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between")
                div(class="min-w-0")
                    h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Ceph 마스터 노드 구성
                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Docker Infra master 노드에 MON/MGR/MDS Ceph container runtime을 먼저 설치하고 구성합니다.
                div(class="flex shrink-0 flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                    button(type="button", (click)="bootstrapMaster()", [disabled]="actionBusy()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                        i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="masterBootstrapBusy() ? 'fa-spinner fa-spin' : 'fa-server'")
                        span 마스터 노드 설치 및 구성

        section(*ngIf="isActiveTab('overview')", class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4", data-testid="storage-dashboard-metrics")
            div(*ngFor="let metric of dashboardMetrics()", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-4 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                    div(class="min-w-0")
                        p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{metric.label}}
                        p(class="mt-2 break-words text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{metric.value}}
                    span(class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-md border", [ngClass]="statusClass(metric.status)")
                        i(class="fa-solid text-[13px]", [ngClass]="metric.icon")
                p(class="mt-3 truncate text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{metric.caption}}

        section(*ngIf="isActiveTab('overview')", class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 xl:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.55fr)_minmax(320px,0.45fr)]")
            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900", data-testid="storage-osd-placement")
                div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 px-4 py-3 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between")
                    div(class="min-w-0")
                        div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                            h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") OSD 배치
                            span(class="inline-flex rounded-md bg-zinc-100 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-600 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-300") {{osdPlacementSummary().active}}/{{osdPlacementSummary().total}} active
                            span(class="inline-flex rounded-md bg-zinc-100 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-600 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-300") {{formatBytes(osdPlacementSummary().raw_bytes)}}
                        p(class="mt-1 truncate text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") FSID {{cluster().fsid || '-'}}
                div(class="border-t border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                    div(class="h-2 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800")
                        div(class="h-full rounded-full bg-zinc-950 transition-all dark:bg-zinc-100", [style.width.%]="capacityUsagePercent()")
                    div(class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-xs")
                        div
                            p(class="font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Raw
                            p(class="mt-1 truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{formatBytes(capacity().raw_bytes)}}
                        div
                            p(class="font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Usable
                            p(class="mt-1 truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{formatBytes(capacity().usable_bytes)}}
                        div
                            p(class="font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Used
                            p(class="mt-1 truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{formatBytes(capacity().used_bytes)}}
                div(class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800", data-testid="storage-cluster-server-list")
                    div(*ngFor="let node of storageNodeRows()", class="px-4 py-4")
                        div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between")
                            div(class="min-w-0")
                                div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                    span(class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-md border", [ngClass]="statusClass(nodeOsdState(node))")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-hard-drive text-[13px]")
                                    div(class="min-w-0")
                                        p(class="truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{node.name || node.host || node.id}}
                                        p(class="mt-0.5 truncate text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{node.host || node.swarm_node_id || '-'}}
                                    span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(nodeOsdState(node))") {{nodeOsdStateLabel(node)}}
                            button(type="button", title="OSD 슬롯 만들기", aria-label="OSD 슬롯 만들기", (click)="openOsdWizard(node)", [disabled]="actionBusy() || !node.osd_slot_candidate", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-zinc-950 text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:bg-zinc-100 disabled:text-zinc-400 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200 dark:disabled:bg-zinc-800 dark:disabled:text-zinc-500")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-plus")
                        div(class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-xs")
                            div
                                p(class="font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Slots
                                p(class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{nodeOsdSummary(node).total || 0}}
                            div
                                p(class="font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Active
                                p(class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{nodeOsdSummary(node).active || 0}}
                            div
                                p(class="font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Raw
                                p(class="mt-1 truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{formatBytes(nodeOsdSummary(node).raw_bytes)}}
                        div(*ngIf="nodeOsdRows(node).length > 0", class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 md:grid-cols-2")
                            div(*ngFor="let slot of nodeOsdRows(node)", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-3 py-2 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950")
                                div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2")
                                    p(class="truncate text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{slot.slot_name || slotOsdLabel(slot)}}
                                    span(class="rounded-md border px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(slot.status)") {{slot.status}}
                                p(class="mt-1 truncate text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{slotOsdLabel(slot)}} · {{slot.size_gb || 0}}GB · {{backingLabel(slot)}}
                        div(*ngIf="nodeOsdRows(node).length === 0", class="mt-3 rounded-md border border-dashed border-zinc-200 px-3 py-3 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-400") OSD 슬롯 없음
                    div(*ngIf="storageNodeRows().length === 0", class="px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Swarm 스토리지 서버가 없습니다.
            div(class="space-y-4")
                div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                    div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Health
                        span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(health().status)") {{healthLabel()}}
                    div(class="px-4 py-3")
                        p(class="text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{healthCaption()}}
                div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                    div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Ceph daemon
                        span(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-500") {{clusterStatusLabel()}}
                    div(class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800")
                        div(*ngFor="let daemon of daemonItems()", class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 px-4 py-3")
                            div(class="min-w-0")
                                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{daemon.label}}
                                p(class="mt-1 truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{daemon.value}}
                            span(class="rounded-md border px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(daemon.status)") {{daemon.status}}
                div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                    div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 위험 경고
                        span(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-500") {{warnings().length || 0}}개
                    div(class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800")
                        div(*ngFor="let warning of warnings()", class="flex gap-3 px-4 py-3")
                            span(class="mt-0.5 inline-flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-md border", [ngClass]="warningClass(warning.level)")
                                i(class="fa-solid text-[13px]", [ngClass]="warningIcon(warning.level)")
                            div(class="min-w-0")
                                p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{warning.title}}
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{warning.message}}
                        div(*ngIf="warnings().length === 0", class="px-4 py-8 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 표시할 경고가 없습니다.

div(*ngIf="preflightModalOpen()", class="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-6")
    div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-950/55", (click)="closePreflightModal()")
    section(class="relative z-10 flex max-h-[88vh] w-full max-w-6xl flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white shadow-xl dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950", data-testid="storage-preflight-modal")
        div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            div(class="min-w-0")
                h2(class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Ceph 사전 점검
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 점검 결과, 실행 과정, warning/error 원인과 보정 방법을 함께 확인합니다.
            button(type="button", (click)="closePreflightModal()", [disabled]="preflightBusy()", class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 text-zinc-600 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 dark:hover:bg-zinc-900")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
        div(class="overflow-auto px-5 py-5")
            div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,0.95fr)_minmax(360px,1.05fr)]")
                div(class="space-y-4")
                    div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            div
                                h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 결과 요약
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{preflight()?.status || (preflightBusy() ? 'running' : 'not_run')}}
                            span(class="rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(preflight()?.status || (preflightBusy() ? 'pending' : 'unknown'))") {{preflight()?.status || (preflightBusy() ? 'running' : 'not_run')}}
                        div(class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 px-4 py-4")
                            div(class="rounded-md bg-zinc-50 px-3 py-3 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 후보
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{preflightSummary().swarm_candidates || 0}}
                            div(class="rounded-md bg-zinc-50 px-3 py-3 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 통과
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{preflightSummary().eligible || 0}}
                            div(class="rounded-md bg-zinc-50 px-3 py-3 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") warning
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{preflightSummary().warning_checks || 0}}
                            div(class="rounded-md bg-zinc-50 px-3 py-3 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") error
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{preflightSummary().failed_checks || 0}}
                    div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            div
                                h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 중간 과정
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") operation output 기준
                            button(type="button", (click)="refreshOperation()", [disabled]="!operationDetail()?.id", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right")
                                span 갱신
                        div(class="max-h-72 overflow-auto px-4 py-3")
                            div(*ngIf="preflightBusy()", class="flex items-center gap-2 py-3 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-spinner fa-spin")
                                span 사전 점검을 실행하는 중입니다.
                            div(*ngIf="!preflightBusy() && operationOutput().length === 0", class="py-8 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 아직 기록된 중간 과정이 없습니다.
                            div(*ngFor="let item of operationOutput()", class="mb-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-50 px-3 py-2 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-300")
                                p(class="font-semibold") {{item.stream || 'system'}}
                                p(class="mt-1 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words") {{item.message}}
                div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800")
                    div(class="border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Warning / Error 보정 안내
                        p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 각 요소별 원인과 수동/자동 보정 가능 여부
                    div(class="max-h-[58vh] overflow-auto")
                        div(*ngIf="preflightIssueRows().length === 0 && !preflightBusy()", class="px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 표시할 warning/error가 없습니다.
                        div(*ngFor="let issue of preflightIssueRows()", class="border-t border-zinc-100 px-4 py-4 first:border-t-0 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                                div(class="min-w-0")
                                    p(class="truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{issue.scope}} · {{issue.title}}
                                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{issue.id}}
                                span(class="shrink-0 rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(issue.status)") {{issue.status}}
                            div(class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-2")
                                div(class="rounded-md bg-zinc-50 px-3 py-2 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                    p(class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 왜 떴나요
                                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300") {{issue.reason || issue.message}}
                                div(class="rounded-md bg-zinc-50 px-3 py-2 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                    p(class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 어떻게 보정하나요
                                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300") {{issue.remediation || '상세 상태를 확인한 뒤 다시 점검하세요.'}}
                            div(class="mt-3 flex justify-end")
                                button(*ngIf="issue.auto_fix?.available", type="button", (click)="fixPreflightIssue(issue)", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles")
                                    span {{autoFixLabel(issue)}}
                                span(*ngIf="!issue.auto_fix?.available", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-400 dark:border-zinc-800") 자동 적용 없음
        div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 border-t border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            p(class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 위험한 host 변경은 자동 적용하지 않고, 안전한 이동/재점검 액션만 제공합니다.
            div(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                button(type="button", (click)="runPreflight()", [disabled]="preflightBusy()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                    i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="preflightBusy() ? 'fa-spinner fa-spin' : 'fa-rotate-right'")
                    span 다시 점검
                button(type="button", (click)="closePreflightModal()", [disabled]="preflightBusy()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                    span 닫기

div(*ngIf="operationModalOpen()", class="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-6")
    div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-950/55", (click)="closeOperationModal()")
    section(class="relative z-10 flex max-h-[88vh] w-full max-w-4xl flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white shadow-xl dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950", data-testid="storage-operation-modal")
        div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            div(class="min-w-0")
                h2(class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 실행 결과
                p(class="mt-1 truncate text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{operationDetail()?.type || 'storage.cluster.*'}} · {{operationDetail()?.status || '대기'}}
            div(class="flex shrink-0 items-center gap-2")
                button(type="button", (click)="refreshOperation()", [disabled]="!operationDetail()?.id", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-900")
                    i(class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right")
                    span 갱신
                button(type="button", (click)="closeOperationModal()", class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 text-zinc-600 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 dark:hover:bg-zinc-900")
                    i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
        div(class="overflow-auto px-5 py-5")
            div(*ngIf="!operationDetail()", class="py-12 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 아직 실행된 storage operation이 없습니다.
            div(*ngIf="operationDetail()", class="space-y-2")
                div(*ngFor="let item of operationOutput()", class="rounded-md bg-zinc-50 px-3 py-2 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-300")
                    p(class="font-semibold") {{item.stream || 'system'}}
                    p(class="mt-1 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words") {{item.message}}
                div(*ngIf="operationOutput().length === 0", class="py-12 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") operation 출력이 아직 없습니다.

div(*ngIf="osdWizardOpen()", class="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-6")
    div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-950/55", (click)="closeOsdWizard()")
    section(class="relative z-10 flex max-h-[88vh] w-full max-w-5xl flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white shadow-xl dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950", data-testid="storage-osd-wizard")
        div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            div(class="min-w-0")
                h2(class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") OSD 슬롯 구성 마법사
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{osdWizardTitle()}} 서버에 Ceph container runtime과 OSD slot을 구성합니다.
            button(type="button", (click)="closeOsdWizard()", [disabled]="osdBusy()", class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 text-zinc-600 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 dark:hover:bg-zinc-900")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
        div(class="overflow-auto px-5 py-5")
            div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 lg:grid-cols-[380px_minmax(0,1fr)]")
                div(class="space-y-4")
                    div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 p-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 대상 서버
                        p(class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200") {{osdWizardTitle()}}
                        p(class="mt-1 break-all text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") swarm_node_id: {{osdTarget()?.swarm_node_id || '-'}}
                    div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 p-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 슬롯 크기
                        div(class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-3 gap-2")
                            button(*ngFor="let size of slotSizeOptions", type="button", (click)="selectOsdSize(size)", [disabled]="osdBusy()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center justify-center rounded-md border text-sm font-semibold disabled:opacity-60", [ngClass]="osdSlotSize() === size ? 'border-zinc-950 bg-zinc-950 text-white dark:border-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950' : 'border-zinc-300 bg-white text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800'")
                                | {{size}}GB
                    div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 p-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                            div
                                h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 슬롯 개수
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 최대 {{osdMaxSlotCount()}}개까지 구성 가능
                            span(class="rounded-md bg-zinc-100 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200") {{osdSlotCount()}}개
                        div(class="mt-3 flex items-center gap-2")
                            button(type="button", aria-label="슬롯 개수 줄이기", (click)="changeOsdSlotCount(-1)", [disabled]="osdBusy() || osdSlotCount() <= 1", class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-minus")
                            input(type="number", data-testid="storage-osd-slot-count", min="1", [attr.max]="osdMaxSlotCount() || null", [ngModel]="osdSlotCount()", (ngModelChange)="setOsdSlotCount($event)", [disabled]="osdBusy() || osdMaxSlotCount() <= 0", class="h-9 min-w-0 flex-1 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50")
                            button(type="button", aria-label="슬롯 개수 늘리기", (click)="changeOsdSlotCount(1)", [disabled]="osdBusy() || osdMaxSlotCount() <= 0 || osdSlotCount() >= osdMaxSlotCount()", class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-plus")
                    div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 p-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 자동 슬롯 산정
                        div(*ngIf="osdBusy() && !osdPlan()", class="mt-3 flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                            i(class="fa-solid fa-spinner fa-spin")
                            span 서버 용량과 OSD 후보를 확인하는 중입니다.
                        div(*ngIf="osdPlan()", class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-2 gap-2")
                            div(*ngFor="let item of osdCapacityItems()", class="rounded-md bg-zinc-50 px-3 py-3 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2")
                                    p(class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{item.label}}
                                    i(class="fa-solid text-[11px] text-zinc-400", [ngClass]="item.icon")
                                p(class="mt-1 truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{formatBytes(item.value)}}
                        div(*ngIf="osdPlan()", class="mt-3 rounded-md border px-3 py-2 text-xs", [ngClass]="osdPlan()?.eligible ? statusClass('ready') : statusClass('warning')")
                            p(class="font-semibold") {{osdPlan()?.message}}
                            p(class="mt-1 break-all") 자동 대상: {{osdTargetPath()}}
                div(class="space-y-4")
                    div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            div
                                h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 작업 plan
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") plan 확인 후에만 실제 OSD slot을 생성합니다.
                            button(type="button", (click)="createOsdPlan()", [disabled]="osdBusy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="osdBusy() ? 'fa-spinner fa-spin' : 'fa-list-check'")
                                span Plan
                        div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 px-4 py-4 md:grid-cols-2")
                            div(*ngFor="let row of osdPlanRows()", class="rounded-md bg-zinc-50 px-3 py-2 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                p(class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{row.label}}
                                p(class="mt-1 break-all text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{row.value}}
                        div(class="border-t border-zinc-200 px-4 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            h4(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 실행 단계
                            div(class="mt-2 space-y-2")
                                div(*ngFor="let step of osdPlan()?.steps || []", class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-[11px] text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-300")
                                    span {{step}}
                                div(*ngIf="!osdPlan()", class="text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 아직 plan을 만들지 않았습니다.
                    div(class="rounded-md border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-amber-800 dark:border-amber-900/70 dark:bg-amber-950/40 dark:text-amber-200")
                        p(class="font-semibold") 되돌릴 수 없는 디스크 작업
                        p(class="mt-1 leading-5") 이 단계는 대상 서버에서 OSD backing block device, Ceph container 기반 `ceph-volume`, OSD daemon service를 구성합니다.
        div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 border-t border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            p(class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") host에 Ceph package를 설치하지 않고 Docker image로 실행합니다.
            div(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                button(type="button", (click)="closeOsdWizard()", [disabled]="osdBusy()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800") 닫기
                button(type="button", (click)="createOsdSlot()", [disabled]="osdCreateDisabled()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                    i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="osdBusy() ? 'fa-spinner fa-spin' : 'fa-hard-drive'")
                    span 생성 및 활성화
